  author={Mongeon, Kevin and Hedlund, David and Ryan Spalding},
  title       = "Analytics in the Sport Industry",
  editor      = "Paul Pedersen and Lucie Thibault",
  booktitle   = "Contemporary Sport Management (Sixth Edition)",
  publisher   = "Human Kinetics",
  address     = "Champaign, IL",
  year        = 2017,
  abstract = {In this chapter, we explain the sports analytics process, discuss how analytics are used in player acquisitions, coaching and sports business, identify emerging trends, and discuss the role of technology in enabling the rapid growth of sports analytics. Readers learn about sports analytics techniques and technologies and learn how metrics are derived and how to evaluate their effectiveness.},
